209
00:16:42.440 --> 00:16:44.000
Hej Fez, oćeš pivo?

210
00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:46.160
Naravno.

211
00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:54.400
Džeki! Šta si uradila sa mojom sobom?

212
